field.finalPrompt.description: The final drawing פרומפט used to צור the תמונה

field.elements.description: The drawing סגנון used to צור the תמונה

description.model.message: Select the מודל for generating images; 'General' is suitable for most scenarios, 'Niji' is suitable for anime סגנון.

description.loop.message: Enable looping for the generated ווידאו.

description.aspect.message: יחס, change the יחס ממדים of the generated תמונה; the default value depends on the מודל and mode.
description.aspect.description: Description of the יחס ממדים פרמטר

description.elements.message: Select the סגנון elements for generating the תמונה.

description.chaos.message: chaos, adjust the degree of variation in the generated תמונה; the higher the number, the more unique and unexpected the generated תמונה will be, range is 0 100, default is 1.

description.fast.message: Ignore current settings and run a single generation משימה in 'fast mode'; no default value.

description.iw.message: iw, set the importance of the תמונה פרומפט relative to the text פרומפט during the generation process; range is 0 2, default is 1.

description.no.message: no, indicates the generation system to try to exclude certain elements; for example, 'no plants' will attempt to צור an תמונה without plants; no default value.
description.no.description: Description of the exclusion פרמטר, translate to 'Exclude'

description.quality.message: איכות, set the איכות and rendering זמן of the generated תמונה; range is .25, .5, or 1, default is 1.

description.random.message: Add random base סגנון codes to the פרומפט; you can use 'סגנון random 16', 'סגנון random 64', or 'סגנון random 128' for different lengths of random סגנון effects; no default value.

description.relax.message: Override current settings and run a single משימה in 'relax mode'; no default value.

description.repeat.message: repeat, create multiple tasks from a single פרומפט; range is 1 40, default is 1.

description.seed.message: Seed, the starting visual noise for generating the תמונה; range is 0 4294967295, default is randomly generated.

description.stop.message: stop, stop the משימה ב־ any stage of the generation process, range 10 100, default is 100 (i.e., fully generated)

description.style.message: סגנון, switch between different versions or styles of the Midjourney or Niji models, such as raw, cute, expressive, original, scenic, default value depends on the מודל and mode

description.stylize.message: stylize, adjust the strength of the Midjourney default aesthetic סגנון applied in the generation משימה, range 0 1000, default is 100

description.tile.message: tile, צור images that can be used to create seamless tiles, no default value

description.turbo.message: Override current settings and run a single משימה in 'Turbo mode', no default value

description.weird.message: weird, explore unusual aesthetic styles with experimental nature, range 0 3000, default is 0

description.imageUrl.message: In ווידאו creation tasks, an תמונה must be uploaded.

description.endImageUrl.message: In ווידאו creation tasks, you can specify an תמונה to be used as the end פריים.
description.endImageUrl.description: Description of the 'end Image Url' פרמטר

description.imageUrl2.message: In tasks creating descriptive images, an תמונה must be uploaded.

description.translation.message: Enable automatic translation during the generation process, non Chinese content will be automatically translated to English input for Midjourney

description.imageWeight.message: iw, adjust the weight of the תמונה פרומפט relative to the text פרומפט, range 0 2, default is 1
description.imageWeight.description: Description of the תמונה weight פרמטר

description.niji.message: niji, when enabled, generated images will use the Niji מודל to create anime סגנון images

description.uploadReferences.message: העלאה images as references for generation, supports up to 5 images. If more than one תמונה is uploaded, they will be automatically merged
description.uploadReferences.description: Description of the העלאה references פרמטר

description.raw.message: raw, when enabled, generated images will use the Midjourney מודל to create raw סגנון images

description.prompt.message: Enter the command; if additional פרמטרים are added, they will override the default preset פרמטרים, for example, adding 'stylize 200' will force the final command to use 'stylize 200'
